Forgetting Customer Goals.

People hate sales talk. And generic ads are full of it.

1. Focus on customer's needs
2. Scan Search Queries
3. Incorporate what they're looking for into your headlines

Tailored ad copy that speaks to their interests will instantly improve your CTR.

Keyword stuffing

Don't stuff keywords in the ad copy as it can :

- Confuse the algorithm
- Make your ads look spammy
- Mismatch your ads with irrelevant queries.

Run multiple variants and use actual phrases that are relevant to what people are searching.
